<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202241>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Manonichthys scintilla, USNM 382744, paratype, 31.5 mm SL, Apo Reef, Mindoro Province, Philippines. (Photo by J. T. Williams)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202242>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Distribution records for species of Manonichthys: M. alleni (black squares), M. jamali (green square), M. paranox (black dots), M. polynemus (red squares), M. scintilla (white squares), M. splendens (black triangles) and M. winterbottomi (red triangle) (based in part on Gill, 2004: fig. 14)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202242/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202243>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Photo of probable juvenile Manonichthys winterbottomi, Moalboal, Cebu, Philippines. (Photo by H. R. Lubbock)." ;
